    "EnvDropout [6] creates the augmentation data by mimicking unseen scenes via an environmental dropout scheme.",
    "AuxRN [9] designs multiple self-supervised auxiliary training tasks to exploit rich semantic information in the environment.",
    "OAAM [30] designs a new model structure and loss for separately processing the mentioned objects and actions in the instructions.Recent VLN works employ cross-modal pretraining paradigms and models for enhancing the modality alignment [15], [16], [24], [31], [32], [33], [34].",
    "HAMT [16] introduces a history-aware multimodal transformer to encode the long-horizon navigation history.",
    "DUET [24] builds a dual-scale graph transformer to jointly perform longterm action planning and fine-grained cross-modal understanding."
